high_descs: Turn around, walk to the door, then turn right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the butter knife in the left corner of the table.
Turn right, walk forward, then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, slice the apple inside, close the door.
Step back to be centered with the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the knife in front of the apple, close the door.
Step forward to come closer to the microwave.
Open the door, pick up a slice of apple, close the door.
Turn right , walk forward, turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the apple to inside, close the door.  Wait a few seconds and remove the apple from the fridge.
Turn left and return to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the apple to the right of the other apple, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of apple in the fridge, place it inside the microwave.
